</a>的后续作品。他们使用了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a>的“Nevermind”和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fleetwood-mac">Fleetwood Mac</a>的“Rumours”的音板。</p><p> “它既便宜又开放，”贝斯手格斯·罗默笑着说。 “我认为我们中没有人真正关心过这是喷火战机工作室这个事实。 “我认为尊重这类东西的人不会创作出最好的艺术品。” </p><figure id="attachment_3760167" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3760167" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3760167" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Amyl-and-The-Sniffers-performing.jpg" alt="Amyl and the Sniffers 乐队的艾米·泰勒 (Amy Taylor) 在 2023 年 Forwards Festival 的舞台上表演。（摄影：Mike Lewis Photography/Redferns）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Amyl-and-The-Sniffers-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Amyl-and-The-Sniffers-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Amyl-and-The-Sniffers-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Amyl-and-The-Sniffers-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Amyl-and-The-Sniffers-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Amyl-and-The-Sniffers-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3760167" class="wp-caption-text"> Amyl and the Sniffers 乐队的艾米·泰勒 (Amy Taylor) 在 2023 年 Forwards Festival 的舞台上表演。（摄影：Mike Lewis Photography/Redferns）</figcaption></figure><p>至于《Jerkin》的灵感来源，泰勒告诉<em>《NME》</em> ：“啊，到处都是一堆垃圾。操大家！”</p><p>相关新闻称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/amyl-the-sniffers-announce-biggest-show-yet-at-london-alexandra-palace-buy-tickets-3801835">Amyl &amp; The Sniffer 乐队将于明年在伦敦亚历山德拉宫举办迄今为止规模最大的头条演出</a>。下个月，他们将开始英国和爱尔兰之旅，然后前往欧洲各地。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/amyl-and-the-sniffers-tickets/artist/5261691?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliat